e":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T04:53:33.000Z","msg":"有好多人學校成績唔好<br />\n靠果幾個月溫書考試<br />\n如果考唔到都幾慘<br />\n晒左一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e24a0ff4c0cc3029f26953948c11c7d48ed56987","tid":1989473,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"741a6240e94e38ebe2889dd9d4591d13a2fe385d","tid":1989473,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"382f8dab2c2e8589aba9d760d12c11fc342d97b2","tid":1989473,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T04:48:49.000Z","msg":"戴豬咀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T04:50:17.000Z","msg":"如果考3個鐘都咪話唔辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T04:53:53.000Z","msg":"人地個filter係高級野黎<br />\n舒服過你戴N95"},{"pid":"bbcadc9a13e4d5c76f5d725d1a0739e8ba3082a1","tid":1989473,"uid":297102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T04:58:12.000Z","msg":"屌你老母港共政府無人性"}]}